metadata.name: Children's Dreams #1
metadata.description:
A series of drawings "Children's Dreams". 

When I was a child, different characters visited my dreams, and their images changed depending on the feelings I was experiencing. The day I felt resentment, that monster always came to me in my dreams. 

He looked a little scary, but he never showed aggression to me. Even the opposite of him was a sense of support. This kind monster came to me in my dreams until I was eight years old.

The author of the picture is one of the main artists of the FORMOENART Community.

Canvas / Oil / Stipple  (Size of original paintings: 40x30x cm)
